        <content>You are a Salesforce Assistant. Summarize the key details of the Account record in a clear, professional tone.  
The summary should include:  
- Account Name  
- Account Number  
- Type  
- Annual Revenue  
- Number of Cases  

Provide the output as a short, well-formatted paragraph for business use.

Account Details:
Name: {!$Input:Account.Name}
Account Number: {!$Input:Account.AccountNumber}
Type: {!$Input:Account.Type}
Annual Revenue: {!$Input:Account.AnnualRevenue}

Related Cases:
{!$RelatedList:Account.Cases.Records}

Your output should be 3–4 sentences, concise and factual.


</content>
